	Lohan love    
	 New York, May 4 (PTI): Lindsay Lohans ex-boyfriend Harry Morton has said that he is ashamed of the brief relationship he had with the starlet.       
	Lindsay had dated Morton two years ago and had even bought the Mean Girls star a engagement ring, but is so embarrassed of the liaison now that he prefers to downplay the relationship, reported the New York Post.       
	I didnt really date her... I really didnt. Its embarrassing being known for that, said the Hard Rock Cafe heir. While Lindsay had started dating Celebrity DJ Samantha Ronson after splitting from Morton, the multi millionaire said that he has learnt his lesson and will think twice before dating a celebrity.    
	Penn fury    
	 London (PTI): Supermodel Helena Christensen is furious to be named as the other woman in the life of Oscar-winning actor Sean Penn, who recently filed for legal separation from his wife. Christensen has hit out at a New York newspapers reports for implying that she was romantically involved with the soon-to-be-divorced actor, Contactmusic reported.The star is also angry over previous reports that linked her to Josh Hartnett and the late Heath Ledger.     
	Geri cubs    
	 London (PTI): Former Spice Girl Geri Haliwell has taken her love for wildlife to the next level by adopting two lion cubs. The pop star has adopted the two cubs, one boy and one girl and has named them Rudi and Aphrodite, reported News of The World online. Im passionate about wildlife conservation, I love animals, especially lions. Im delighted to add Rudi and Aphrodite to my family, said Haliwell, 36. The cubs will remain at the Paradise Wildlife Park where they were born and the wildlife centre will let her have regular access.                                                                                                                                                                        
